`,S.jsxs(t.p,{children:["The ",S.jsx(t.code,{children:"RadioGroup"})," component lets users select a single option from a list. Built on top of MUI's ",S.jsx(t.code,{children:"RadioGroup"}),", it adds responsive layout switching, group-level disable, required state, and custom Figma-spec radio icons."]}),`
